Name: Rambunny
About the game: When a quiet family of rabbits is abducted by evil space foxes, only a brave rabbit can help. Join in an adventure with hidden traps, escape from a fireball rains, drive a scooter, face a giant fox robot, explore caves, fly in a rocket and defeat the evil boss to bring the bunnies home! Rambunny is a 2D platform game with moderate difficulty, containing 10 stages divided into small dungeons. Want More!?
